reviews.review_text: will make you smile So this is the only recording of this improptu event without a review right now. Must rectify that! Love how prominent the vocals are here, as well as Jerry’s guitar. No way you can hear the Jam on this recording and not smile. What fun was had on this night next to the Grand Canyon of the East!
